data.description: Stunning custom ranch style Scheumack home located on 5.5 acres in the popular oak studded Westpark Estates subdivision. The home features 4 large bedrooms, 3.5 baths; one of which is fully handicap accessible. There is an abundance of storage space throughout the home. Spacious covered patio with access from kitchen/dining area.  Adjacent to the home is a large two-story horse barn and stable including a workshop with cement floors and built in cabinets as well as, a storage area/hay loft. In addition, a dirt floor tractor barn with electricity is located on the back side of the property. Property is fully fenced for large animals with lots of grazing area. The home also features a new water heater, a well with a commercial pump, roof that was replaced in 2017 and 4 year old HVAC units. Rare find in this day and time, call today for your private showing.
